Package: grafito
Version: 1.0.0-beta
Section: graphics
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0
Maintainer: Grafito Team <grafito@example.com>
Description: Mathematical function graphing calculator
 Grafito is a modern, high-performance mathematical graphing calculator
 built with Rust. It supports 2D and 3D function plotting, parametric
 curves, implicit curves, ODE solving, and much more.
 .
 Features:
  - 2D and 3D function plotting
  - Parametric curves and surfaces
  - Implicit curves (contour plots)
  - ODE system solving
  - Piecewise functions
  - Modern GTK interface
Homepage: https://github.com/Diez111/Grafito
